title: Mapping Notation
text: Each arrow matches the person to their Student ID.

title: Creating Ordered Pairs
text: We create ordered pairs with the person’s name as the x-value and their Student ID as the y-value. We get {(Khan Nguyen, kn68413), (Abigail Brown, ab56781), (Sumantha Mishal, sm32479), (Jose Hernandez, jh47983)}
